# Application Deployment – VLC Media Player (Microsoft Intune)

## Objective

Deploy a Microsoft Store application using Microsoft Intune and validate successful installation on a managed Windows endpoint.

---

## Environment

Platform: Microsoft Intune (Endpoint Manager)  
Application Type: Microsoft Store App (New)  
Application: VLC Media Player  
Publisher: VideoLAN  
Device: INTUNEWIN11_01 (Windows 11 Hyper-V VM)  
Assignment Method: Required deployment to INTUNE-Test-Devices group  

---

## Configuration Steps

Application created within Intune:

Path:

Intune Admin Center → Apps → Windows → Add → Microsoft Store app (new)

Steps performed:

- Selected VLC Media Player from Microsoft Store catalog
- Configured application details and description
- Assigned application as Required to test device group

Screenshot:

![VLC App Overview](../screenshots/15-app-overview-vlc-created.png)

---

## Deployment Execution

After assignment:

- Device powered on
- Manual sync initiated
- Microsoft Intune Management Extension triggered installation

Screenshot:

![App Install Notification](../screenshots/16-app-install-notification-success.png)

---

## Deployment Monitoring

Installation status monitored through Intune:

Path:

Intune Admin Center → Apps → Monitor → Device install status

Screenshot:

![Device Install Success](../screenshots/17-app-device-install-success.png)

---

## Endpoint Validation

Final validation performed directly on managed device:

- VLC Media Player present on desktop
- Application launched successfully
- Installation confirmed functional

Screenshot:

![VLC Installed Locally](../screenshots/18-device-vlc-installed-local.png)

---

## Troubleshooting Encountered

Initial installation status remained pending until device synchronization was triggered manually.  
After sync, Intune processed deployment successfully.

---

## Outcome

Successfully demonstrated:

- Microsoft Store app deployment through Intune
- Required application assignment
- Deployment monitoring and validation
- Endpoint-level verification of installation

This phase completes the application lifecycle portion of the endpoint management lab.
